caption: To be honest when Jack and Jack first had music released I stayed inside my house for a while until I had all of the words memorized and I actually missed my school bus once. ?They are honestly my favorite. no matter what they did I instantly fell in love. There are times where people have opportunities in life and I'm so happy they took theirs. Looking back at when they were first at magcon to now seeing them at events with huge audiences make me feel so proud of them. Knowing  this is only the beginning makes me feel so excited because I can imagine it now, hearing them on the radio everyday and seeing their albums all around the stores worldwide. They amaze me more and more each day. I can't wait for the future. They mean the world to me #contest #contest #contest #contest
